{{TagLine|AC1200 Enterprise Mesh WiFi System}} :{{ProductPage|https://www.ip-com.com.cn/en/product/EW9.html}} "10036286" and "V1.1" is silkscreened on the board in FCC photos. {{See also|Tenda Mesh3|Tenda Mesh3-18|Tenda}} The FCC entry also covers a version of the [[IP-COM EP9]] which is identical except that :it is missing the RJ-45 ports for LAN/WAN and the associated [[Realtek]] switch chip. The [[IP-COM EP9|EP9]] was later re-designed to simplify the design and lower costs by completely :removing the switch-related circuitry and it was re-certified under its own FCC ID. Two of the four RJ-45 ports can be configured for WAN or LAN. ===See also=== :[[List of Wireless Systems]] *[[IP-COM EP9]] *[[IP-COM EW9]] __NOTOC__
